---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions — Breakthru" description="Terms and conditions for Breakthru online personal training services.">
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-sm opacity-50 mb-10">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By purchasing or accessing any Breakthru programme, subscription, or content, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, do not use our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Services</h2>
        <p>Breakthru offers online personal training programmes, nutrition plans, and coaching content created by Myer Bevan. All content is for general fitness and wellness purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. Consult a qualified health professional before beginning any exercise or nutrition programme.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Purchases and Payments</h2>
        <p>All prices are listed in USD. One-off programme purchases grant you personal, non-transferable access to that content. Monthly subscriptions are billed on a recurring basis and may be cancelled at any time. No refunds are provided once digital content has been accessed.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Cancellations</h2>
        <p>Monthly subscriptions can be cancelled at any time through your account or by contacting us. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. You will retain access until that date.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Health Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>Breakthru programmes are designed for healthy adults. You participate at your own risk. Breakthru and Myer Bevan accept no liability for injury, illness, or any adverse outcome resulting from following any programme or advice provided through our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content — including programmes, videos, meal plans, and written material — is the intellectual property of Breakthru. You may not reproduce, redistribute, or resell any content without prior written permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of our services after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any questions regarding these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@breakthru.fit" class="link link-hover">hello@breakthru.fit</a>.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
